# Spinner

Use `Spinner` for short loading states inside buttons, panels, overlays, or empty-state variants.

## Basic Usage

### Spinner
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SpinnerSpinnerDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxSpinner />
  </template>
---
:::

